{"tid":1609943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵仿效日本JR推出特急列車，正名為「油塘特急限定」","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:54:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T18:02:50.000Z","uid":206523,"like":90,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"408c7cd331bd5ecc4b65d251409343fae66e6415","tid":1609943,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f2Ce0pL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff2Ce0pL.jpg&h=c698e116&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今日十月一日為國慶日，港鐵積極網民發起的參與「賀佢老母」活動</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">得知年青人熱愛日本文化，因而仿效日本JR服務<br />\n在今晚正式推出特急列車！<br />\n由九龍塘出發，只需10分鐘直達油塘站，比平日節省六成時間！</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">然而，由於技術尚未發展成熟，正式推出時間尚未落實<br />\n不過今日適逢國慶，所以推出限定版本供市民試乘，車費與平日相同！<br />\n未知市民在今晚試搭後感覺如何？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 支持將特急列車恆常化！以後九龍塘上車，下一站就係調景嶺！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要試多幾次先，開得太快可能又壞車，斷開兩截迫人行路軌"},{"pid":"c9ffa278ee43f8477bfe114914016ad10621d1cd","tid":1609943,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:04.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"9481da77285dd6ab0b3a79604ecf8ae0eb56a28c","tid":1609943,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:14.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"63541d1625c4b43f4472867d3da5edb534fad7e9","tid":1609943,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"ab241ad58c05473a4cad9930ed5a74ae265891cc","tid":1609943,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:37.000Z","msg":"推 4/10"},{"pid":"52a65c4846325b39a77d5290de2b01ed78861382","tid":1609943,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"推 5